- **`double`** - Two hinged leaves that meet in center
- **`sliding`** - Horizontal line with directional arrow (thickness 4px)

Window types mentioned in domain model suggest extensibility, but currently only visual difference is in SVG preview. The 3D preview renders both doors and windows as simple boxes with no type-specific geometry differentiation in `buildPreviewObjects.js`.

