### Summary: Key Pipeline

```
Domain Model (window/door object)
         ↓
Wall Preview Context (position calculation on wall)
         ↓
Object Descriptor (createOpeningInsertDescriptor)
  - kind: 'door' | 'window'
  - geometry: 'box'
  - materialKey: 'door' | 'window'
  - size: { x: visibleWidth, y: visibleHeight, z: thickness }
  - baseElevation, angle, rotation
         ↓
Scene Descriptor (buildPreviewScene)
         ↓
Three.js Objects (createBoxObject)
  - THREE.BoxGeometry
  - THREE.Mesh with palette material
  - THREE.EdgesGeometry for outlines
  - Shadow casting enabled
         ↓
Floor Groups (buildPreviewObjectRoot)
         ↓
Three.js Scene (createPreviewViewport)
  - WebGL Renderer
  - Orbit Controls
  - Lighting (Ambient + Hemisphere + Directional)
  - Grid Helper
```

